love walking dead - what can I say

Zombie story, yes.  But so much more.  A 21st C. morality tale of how different individuals face extreme adversity.  As the character Darrell states in season 5, while trying to help the horse 'Buttons':  'the longer one is out here (in the de-evolved world with no government, structure, or steadfast rules) the more one becomes what one is.'  Some characters realize strengths they never knew they possessed, while others disintegrate under the unrelenting new reality.  Superb cast, writing, direction, and yes, the most awesome & creative zombies made to date!

Buyer beware. This is not against the show itself but against the product quality.

I cannot be sure it is any particular seller as I ordered from multiple sellers including Amazon to determine the problem.
Season 3 continues to come as opened and used with fingerprints on the discs. Amazon even tries to hide this by shrink wrapping it but you can tell it is not manufacture wrapped because it is not the stiff wrapping with folded and glued ends like all new movies come, but the stretchy shrink wrap that looks like its for kitchen use.
Beware that the individual season 3 is arriving the same way, opened and used.
